        "client_msg_id": "2ea5dda2-4485-48a6-aa09-9088e98d0d3c",
        "text": "Thank you for the ref. It's been a while since I've done any game\/interactive programming, so I don't know where the tech is!\n\nI would love to experiment with that, but I'm reeeeally watching out for scope creep right now. I've decided that juiciness is fair game, but I'm going to try not to go outside my wheelhouse (where 3-D modeling is) for a while.",
